Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.07,0:46:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.\NOkay, here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.04,0:46:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Yes.\N>> I just wanted to uh thank you for your
