Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.28,0:46:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Yes. God bless you.\N>> Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.88,0:46:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Thank you.\N>> And a picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.04,0:46:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Yeah. And a picture.\N>> Ah, now he brings in the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.04,0:46:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch.\N>> His thumbs are
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.80,0:46:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,>> There you go.\N>> Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.04,0:47:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Thank you.\N>> Hello, Doug. Hello, Susan. Um, I've sat
